## 5.1 Dual Side Flow Compression Chambers

### Purpose

Primary airflow collection structures.

### Responsibilities

* Air capture
* Flow conditioning
* Turbulence moderation
* Pressure generation

### Benefit

Creates two independent pressure sources.

---

## 5.2 Nose Intake Compression Gate

### Purpose

Provides supplemental frontal airflow capture.

### Responsibilities

* Intake regulation
* Flow balancing
* Pressure synchronization

---

## 5.3 Venturi Acceleration Tunnel

### Purpose

Accelerates airflow.

### Responsibilities

* Velocity amplification
* Pressure redistribution
* Flow concentration

### Principle

```text
Large Area
     ↓
Medium Area
     ↓
Small Area
     ↓
Higher Velocity
